# Contacting SPI

To contact SPI, please send email to one of the following:

* the SPI [mailing lists](http://lists.spi-inc.org/listinfo)
* the [SPI Board of Directors](mailto:board@spi-inc.org)
* the [SPI Officers](mailto:officers@spi-inc.org)
(President, VP, Secretary, Treasurer)
* an individual [officer or board member](../corporate/board)
* for press/publicity related questions please contact <press@spi-inc.org>
* For website related questions, please contact <webmaster@spi-inc.org>

You can send mail to SPI at:

